01:31.021 --> 01:32.471
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

01:39.133 --> 01:40.445
Bow your heads.

01:41.722 --> 01:44.587
Father God, thank you
for this family,

01:44.725 --> 01:47.486
this food and your
many blessings.

01:47.624 --> 01:50.213
Bless this food that will nourish
our bodies in your name,

01:50.351 --> 01:52.077
Jesus, as we all say... As we all say...

